OL,3,CMan, 27, appears in court accused of
OL,4,Cmurder
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court accused of
OL,7,Fkilling another man in Abergavenny.
OL,9,FLiam Bennett, 27, appeared at Newport
OL,10,FMagistrates' Court on Saturday (23
OL,11,FMay) charged with the murder of Idris
OL,12,FSquires.
OL,14,FOfficers from Gwent Police were called
OL,15,Fto Old Hereford Road in Abergavenny,
OL,16,Fat around 6.15am on 15 May after a man
OL,17,Fwas left with life-threatening
OL,18,Finjuries. He later died in hospital.
