OL,3,CMan, 27, appears in court accused of
OL,4,Cmurder
OL,6,FOn Saturday, magistrate Wayne Crocker
OL,7,Fsaid Bennett, of Oak Tree Lane,
OL,8,FGilwern, would be remanded into
OL,9,Fcustody ahead of a hearing at Cardiff
OL,10,FCrown Court on Tuesday (26 May).
OL,12,FHe told Bennett: "Your case is now
OL,13,Fgoing to be adjourned and sent to
OL,14,FCardiff Crown Court."
OL,16,FOn Friday, Detective Chief Inspector
OL,17,FEllen Joslyn of Gwent Police said: "We
OL,18,Fwould like to thank the community for
OL,19,Ftheir support whilst we investigate
OL,20,Fthe circumstances of this tragic death.
