OL,3,CMan, 27, appears in court accused of
OL,4,Cmurder
OL,6,F"We understand that reports of this
OL,7,Fnature can be concerning to our
OL,8,Fcommunities.
OL,10,F"While our inquiries continue over the
OL,11,Fcoming days, you are likely to see an
OL,12,Fincreased number of officers in the
OL,13,Farea."
OL,15,FGwent Police is appealing to anyone
OL,16,Fwith dashcam, CCTV or doorbell footage
OL,17,Ffrom Old Hereford Road or Underhill
OL,18,FCrescent and the surrounding area
OL,19,Faround the time of the incident.
